1.0 Files
	Makefile                            Unit tests building rules
	utest__testDataCompiler.c           UTs for the testDataCompiler fabric
	utest__testData_fixedTimePeriod.c   UTs for testData_fixedTimePeriod sub-module
	utest__testData_number.c            UTs for testData_number.c
	utest__testData_squareWave.c        UTs for testData_squareWave.c
	dataViewer.c                        Useful tool to check for the Virtual-SRAM content

2.0 Description
	This directory contains all unit-tests for the testDataCompiler module and its sub-modules.
	
	To build the unit-tests you can use the following syntax, but you need to install cJSON library in your PC, before.
		make [GDB={1|0}]

	[!] In order to mock the SRAM operations calls, I have simulated their functionalities with a binary file
	    (/tmp/testDataCompiler.foo). For a better check for the testDataCompiler_generate() results, you can read the file
	    content.
	    In this case I suggest you to use "ghex" tool.
